pkgdesc="ACPI scripts for EeePC netbook computers (700, 701, 900, 900A, 901, 904HD, S101, 1000, 1000H, 1000HD, 1000HE, 1005HA, 1005-HA-H, 1005PE, 1005P, 1008HA, 1201N, T91MT)"
